        <num>CC 881</num>
        <heading>881.  Representation: effect</heading>
        <content>
          <p>Art. 881.  Representation: effect
Representation is a fiction of the law, the effect of which is to put the representative in the place, degree, and rights of the person represented.</p>
        </content>
